Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過這座山之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 港口之都 哈里 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從 哈里 可以搭船到相鄰的 拉克爾 大陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克爾 那裡有大型的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以找到能解讀這本古文書的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有些什麼重要的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是在怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟 你是劍士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也進去幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才啊 有一位旅行的劍士為了消滅邪惡的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到洞窟裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡的魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都出現在牧場 還把動物吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我養的牲畜全被吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他是劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人進去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們也進去幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 真是些強人所難的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦哪 克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有困難的人我們也不能不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是好心人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊… 看你們的囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什麼樣的魔物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是能吃掉牛羊的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是非常巨大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險 快出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把村子裡的牧場一一搗毀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把他們辛苦養大的家畜吃掉的邪惡魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 艾修頓·安卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替天行道 制裁你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種魔物我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾、蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～兩位還真親熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 龍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是怕了本艾修頓大爺 逃之夭夭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你們那是什麼眼神啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你背上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會粘在我的背上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快幫我拿下來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～誰來救我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你們害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛把責任都推到我們頭上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我全力保護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果無法集中精神戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒有保護到誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎完全融合在一起的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用蕾娜的治愈能力恢复不了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況的話就有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴的紋章術能不能幫幫他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒聽說過有那樣的紋章術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候玩捉迷藏每次都是我扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠足的當天一定會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一走在路上就會踩到屎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我總是背負這種厄運呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜它所賜總是碰到災難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果都沒人肯陪我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～那麼你是孤單一個人出來旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說孤單一個人～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡一個人旅行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就有新同伴了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的同伴哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以變成這樣都是你們害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要負起責任吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦法倒是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前看到過一本書上面是這麼記載的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍附身者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以飛舞在天空的王者之淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來淨化其身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛舞在天空的王者之淚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有王者之淚者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寧靜的水面所環抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶如母親體內一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其降臨的險峻山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受榮耀的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得勝利之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝方可得到王者之淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時詠誦誓詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著強烈且痛苦的咆哮聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔龍將從世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到飛舞在天空的王者之淚就行了 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寧靜的水面所環抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶如母親體內一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是位於克洛斯大陸西北方的\N克爾湖的山嶽神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點往那個神殿出發吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～龍龍它們在吃蛋糕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 可不可以給它們取名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只眼睛瞪得長長的就叫"長長"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只眼睛圓溜溜的就叫"圓圓"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們很喜歡耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個傢夥襲擊牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家畜都吃光了耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個真的有襲擊牧場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都說不是了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別上當！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍這種動物是很兇惡的魔物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等等我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一覺得自己實在累得要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這兩個傢夥還真重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只靠我一個人背著你們走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也給我下來走走行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的廢物…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 精神不是超好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剛才那個咖啡店買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也給我一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長長和圓圓也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 你們倆要去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停、停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啦 很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我非找到王者之淚不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要特地跑來找魔物打架吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德 聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我跟魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼巨大的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按理說會有相當的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要循著波動尋找的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以找到他的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南南西的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感應到強大的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安無事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山腳下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長長 圓圓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…想不到我會變成這幅德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太悲哀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…是不是丟下我繼續旅行了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得被這種魔物附身不可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種邪惡的稱呼叫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？誰…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們在說話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我聽錯了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在這種地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 波動非常強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我們已經離他們很近囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長長 圓圓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長長…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物的巢穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德 你看那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 襲擊牧場的原來是這群傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～蟲子～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 討厭啦 討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我到前面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再走下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃哪 閃哪 閃哪 閃哪 閃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓 小心上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群玷污魔族崇高名譽的低賤之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是低級的魔物 竟然趕來惹我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是長長和圓圓它們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔據了艾修頓的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加諸於吾等魔族的的惡名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是你們這些魔物\N所幹出的下流之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種罪行就用你們的死來洗刷吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢夥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空·破·斬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亞倫那時候一樣的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦～蟲子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能洗脫嫌疑真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 村裡的牧場就不會受到襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能走啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上之所以背著這兩坨東東
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把它們弄掉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直跟著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下耳根子又沒的清靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出發咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 克爾湖的山嶽神殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克勞德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在克爾湖的山嶽神殿裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們碰到了一位正在尋找戀人的\N不可思議的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶？和我一樣\N是來自其他星球的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這時真的話\N這個星球的某個地方應該有宇宙船
